message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been designed with exceptional quality and functionality in mind. It's a unique opportunity to own something that truly stands out in its category. Considering its value and the benefits it offers, I would like to propose a price of $120 for this product. I believe it represents an excellent investment for anyone looking to enhance their experience with [brief description of the product's benefits]. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing further details or proceeding with the purchase.
